此地下車站在1937年7月1日，作為跨城線延長段由[[納蘇大道車站_(IND跨城線)|納蘇大道]]延長至[[霍伊特-歇爾美角街車站|霍伊特-歇爾美角街]]時啟用<ref name="bde19370701">{{cite news|title=New Crosstown Subway Line Is Opened|url=https://bklyn.newspapers.com/image/52688792/?terms=crosstown%2Bsubway|accessdate=2015-12-24|publisher=Brooklyn Daily Eagle|date=1937-07-01|archive-date=2021-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211210175517/https://bklyn.newspapers.com/image/52688792/?terms=crosstown%2Bsubway|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此站設有兩個[[側式月台|側式月台]]和兩條軌道<ref name=MTA-GLineReview-Append-2013>{{cite web|title=Review of the G Line: Appendices|url=http://web.mta.info/nyct/service/G_Appendices_7_10_13.pdf|publisher=[[Metropolitan_Transportation_Authority|Metropolitan Transportation Authority]]|accessdate=2015-10-28|date=2013-07-10|archive-date=2016-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160127233038/http://web.mta.info/nyct/service/G_Appendices_7_10_13.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

此站距離跨城線與[[IND福爾頓街線|IND福爾頓街線]]的交匯處相當接近，位於[[拉法葉大道車站_(IND福爾頓街線)|拉法葉大道]]以西，但兩站並無轉乘設定。往[[曼哈頓|曼哈頓]]方向的[[紐約地鐵A線|A線]]與[[紐約地鐵C線|C線]]列車的乘客可在離站後幾秒右側車門看到此站月台。兩站之間還有職員專用的隧道連通。

MTA拒絕一個將此站連往[[大西洋大道-巴克萊中心車站|大西洋大道-巴克萊中心]]的計劃，指兩站之間的步行距離過長<ref name=MTA-GLineReview-2013>{{cite web|title=Review of the G Line|url=http://web.mta.info/nyct/service/G_LineReview_7_10_13.pdf|website=[[Metropolitan_Transportation_Authority|mta.info]]|publisher=[[Metropolitan_Transportation_Authority|Metropolitan Transportation Authority]]|accessdate=2015-08-02|date=2013-07-10|archive-date=2015-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150226002828/http://web.mta.info/nyct/service/G_LineReview_7_10_13.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="DNA-GTrainPush-Dec2012">{{cite web|last1=Hoffman|first1=Meredith|title=G Train Riders to Renew Push for Improved Service With New Year|url=http://www.dnainfo.com/new-york/20121231/williamsburg/g-train-riders-renew-push-for-improved-service-with-new-year|publisher=[[DNAinfo.com|DNAinfo.com]]|accessdate=2015-08-24|location=[[Williamsburg,_Brooklyn|Williamsburg, Brooklyn]]|date=2012-12-31|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160829062726/https://www.dnainfo.com/new-york/20121231/williamsburg/g-train-riders-renew-push-for-improved-service-with-new-year|archivedate=2016-08-29}}</ref>。

